# CVE-2023-45853: zlib minizip zipOpenNewFileInZip4_6 integer overflow.
# This affects the minizip component bundled in Debian's zlib package.
# LaminarDB does not use minizip — only zlib decompression (via libssl3/curl).
# Debian has not patched this in bookworm as minizip is considered optional.
CVE-2023-45853
